<p>
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> mayiṟ cūṭi tannaṭiyiraṇ<unclear>ṭum taṭa</unclear> muṭiyākat tonnilai ventar cūṭa munṉam manuvāṟu perukak kaliyāṟu vaṟuppac ceṅkol ticai to <gap reason="lost" quantity="20" unit="character"/> muṟai niṟpa vilaṅkiya ten <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> piṟkulappiṟai pol niṟpiḻai yennum colletir
